The one single day I ever dared taking DXM during the daytime was when my father decided to take a bunch of painkillers. We were both hiding it from each other.
It was a compulsion that went away on its own after about six months. I guess I got bored of it. I'm lucky it never turned into a full-blown addiction.
Admittedly I had a problem with DXM in my late teens because it was the craziest thing I'd ever done and it shattered my boxed-in worldview. Nobody noticed.
As I get older it's harder to bounce back from a drug trip. After 10 hours of being insane, I just want to be sober again.
I haven't done DXM in a very long time, probably two years. I would like to do it again soon.
It's fun to drink heavily or do a bout of drugs every now and then. Like getting into a video game for a while.
